air-mentor-api/README.md:3:Node/TypeScript backend for the AirMentor admin-foundation slice.
air-mentor-api/README.md:22:The API is backend-only. Opening `http://127.0.0.1:4000/` returns a small API info payload; the admin UI itself should be opened from the frontend dev server, typically `http://127.0.0.1:5173/`.
air-mentor-api/README.md:67:If the UI starts calling routes such as `/api/admin/reminders` and the live API
air-mentor-api/README.md:141:- `AIRMENTOR_LIVE_SYSTEM_ADMIN_IDENTIFIER=sysadmin`
air-mentor-api/README.md:143:- secret `AIRMENTOR_LIVE_SYSTEM_ADMIN_PASSWORD=<live-system-admin-password>`
air-mentor-api/README.md:160:4. Log in on the live site as `sysadmin`.
air-mentor-api/README.md:162:   - `#/admin/faculties/academic_faculty_engineering_and_technology/departments/dept_cse/branches/branch_mnc_btech/batches/batch_branch_mnc_btech_2023`
air-mentor-api/README.md:172:   - `POST /api/admin/proof-runs/:simulationRunId/recompute-risk`
air-mentor-api/README.md:187:1. Log in as `sysadmin`.
air-mentor-api/README.md:190:4. Verify on sysadmin:
air-mentor-api/README.md:233:- `sysadmin` / `admin1234`
