- Arctic remains authenticated and model-visible, but not execution-promoted
- queue progression now stops cleanly on missing status, stale status, or bounded provider wait expiry
- tmux visibility checks now distinguish `present`, `missing`, and `inaccessible` so status inspection does not corrupt live jobs

---
